{"about_the_game":"Para Bellum - Hold the Line is a 3D real time small unit tactics game. Your task is to hold off enemy attacks wave after wave using a variety of different Units and Supports in your arsenal to the best of your abilities in Campaign and Skirmish modes. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/battle.gif?t=1649329761\" /><br><br><strong>UNITS</strong><br>Deploy and order a multitude of different Units including Riflemen, Medics, Machinegunners and Anti-Vehicle Infantry.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/arty.gif?t=1649329761\" /><br><br><strong>SUPPORTS</strong><br>Turn the tide of the battle by calling in support in the forms of Mortar or Air Strikes, Supply Drops and more.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/campaign.gif?t=1649329761\" /><br><br><strong>CAMPAIGN</strong><br>Complete a campaign of 15 unique missions. Units that survive a battle will gain experience and accompany you to your next mission, but be aware - if they get killed, they're lost forever!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/platoon.gif?t=1649329761\" /><br><br><strong>PLATOON</strong><br>Customize your Platoon by requesting new types of Units and Supports. This will help you gain the upper hand in the battlefield.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772920/extras/screenshot-skirmish-small.png?t=1649329761\" /><br><br><strong>SKIRMISH</strong><br>Skirmish mode allows you to play any of the game's maps with customizable settings.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"We held the line!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1772920/bb40a6f89dcf6f5fe59b7ec4c